@startuml System Overview

title Smart Rental System - Use Case Overview

' Actors
actor Admin
actor Tenant

' System Boundary - Simple version
rectangle "Smart Rental Backend System" {

  usecase "Authentication" as Auth
  usecase "Building\nManagement" as Building
  usecase "Room\nManagement" as Room
  usecase "Contract\nManagement" as Contract
  usecase "Invoice\nManagement" as Invoice
  usecase "Other\nOperations" as Others

}

' Relationships
Admin --> Auth
Admin --> Building
Admin --> Room
Admin --> Contract
Admin --> Invoice
Admin --> Others

Tenant --> Auth
Tenant -[dotted]-> Invoice

note right of Admin
  Full Access:
  • 54+ use cases
  • All CRUD operations
  • Bulk operations
  • Statistics & Reports
end note

note left of Tenant
  Limited Access:
  • Login/Register
  • View invoices
  • Reset password
end note

@enduml
